{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B1341P0D1N000014", "chronotag": "1757948558119", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CF14", "numeroOrdreDepot": "14", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B1341P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B1341", "triAmendement": "eaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaag", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795386", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845407", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Lef&#232;vre"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article unique", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. UNIQUE", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE UNIQUE", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1341.asp#D_Article_unique"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer cet article.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement vise &#x00E0; supprimer l&#x2019;article unique, qui remet en cause les conditions d&#x2019;application du r&#x00E9;gime dit &#x00AB; Dutreil &#x00BB;, pr&#x00E9;vu aux articles 787 B et 787 C du Code g&#x00E9;n&#x00E9;ral des imp&#x00F4;ts.</p><p>Ce dispositif permet, sous conditions de conservation et de direction, une exon&#x00E9;ration de 75 % des droits de mutation &#x00E0; titre gratuit lors de la transmission d&#x2019;entreprises. Il constitue un outil fiscal structurant, con&#x00E7;u pour favoriser la p&#x00E9;rennit&#x00E9; des entreprises familiales, &#x00E9;viter leur d&#x00E9;mant&#x00E8;lement lors des successions ou donations, et pr&#x00E9;server l&#x2019;emploi et l&#x2019;activit&#x00E9; &#x00E9;conomique dans les territoires.</p><p>Il est donc propos&#x00E9; de supprimer cette disposition, afin de pr&#x00E9;server la s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; juridique, la stabilit&#x00E9; fiscale et la comp&#x00E9;titivit&#x00E9; des entreprises fran&#x00E7;aises.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-05-23", "datePublication": "2025-05-28", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-05-28T12:18:14+02:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B1341P0D1N000014?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "79468", "typePosition": "Premier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}